Ali Hassanein (13 Jenụwarị 1939 - 12 Ọgọst 2015) bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri.

onye a na-eme ihe nkiri na-arụ ọrụ n'etiti ihe nkiri, ihe nkiri na ọrụ telivishọn na ọnwa nke "aam Zeyiryab" na ihe nkiri ice cream Amr Diab, na Sheikh zaryr na Kit Kat na ihe nkiri nke onye na-ese ihe Mahmoud Abdel Aziz.
Hassanein nwụrụ mgbe ọ dị afọ 76 site na ọrịa kansa imeju n'abali 12 nke ọnwa Ọgọst afọ 2015.
